					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is my latest work, inspired by recent personal events that have transpired in my life. I wanted to combine the feeling of heartache and the joy of music. The songs &quot;Liability&quot; by Lorde and &quot;My Way&quot; by Frank Sinatra were both big components in how this turned out.</p> <p>Oh yeah, the character number for &quot;&lt;&quot; is 60, so technically this is SCP-4 &lt;3</p> <p><strong>Crit Attribution:</strong><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1547679516" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-aers" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1547679516" alt="Dr Aers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-aers" >Dr Aers</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/reverend-fox" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1893953&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1547679516" alt="Reverend Fox" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1893953)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/reverend-fox" >Reverend Fox</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kindlyturtleclem" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4504036&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1547679516" alt="KindlyTurtleClem" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4504036)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.